title: Louis Vuitton Monogram Jacquard CarryAll PM
description: Louis Vuitton CarryAll Nautical PM bag (from around March 2021) in multi-colour monogram jacquard-woven cream canvas. Featuring gold-toned hardware, natural cowhide leather trims and decorative leather lace. The magnetic closure opens to a logo printed textile-lined interior with a detachable zipped pouch, zip pocket & 2 patch pockets.
